==== You receive the error "Error loading the Changeset Comments Policy policy"
This means you do not have the TFS Power Tools installed (or it is the incorrect version).

*Workaround*:

Install the latest version of http://visualstudiogallery.msdn.microsoft.com/c255a1e4-04ba-4f68-8f4e-cd473d6b971f[the TFS Power Tools]

*DO NOT override policy exceptions!*